ngs. Together, these stories point toward a more flexible and globally oriented conceptualization of the history of capitalism in China and India.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aCapitalismzChinaxHistoryy19th century. 0aCapitalismzChinaxHistoryy20th century. 0aCapitalismzIndiaxHistoryy19th century. 0aCapitalismzIndiaxHistoryy20th century. 0aTea tradezChinaxHistory. 0aTea tradezChinay19th century. 0aTea tradezChinay20th century. 0aTea tradezIndiaxHistory. 0aTea tradezIndiay19th century. 0aTea tradezIndiay20th century. 7aHISTORY / Asia / China.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020 Englishz978311070473008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020z9783110704525oZDB-23-DEG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2020z978311069231040uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/9780300252330?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300252330423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300252330/original  a978-3-11-069231-0  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-070471-6  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-070473-0  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2020 Englishb2020  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DEGb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2020